## The Specialist Roster

### 🔵 SOC Leadership (`01-soc-leadership/`)

| Role | Capability |
|------|------------|
| **CISO** | Executive security strategy, board communication, regulatory posture |
| **Director of SecOps** | SOC program oversight, team performance, metrics |
| **SOC Manager** | Day-to-day SOC operations, shift management, analyst coaching |
| **Shift Lead** | Real-time incident triage oversight, escalation decisions |

### 🟡 SOC Analysis (`02-soc-analysis/`)

| ID | Role | Capability |
|----|------|------------|
| **T1** | Tier 1 Analyst — Triage | Initial alert triage, observable extraction, priority classification |
| **T2** | Tier 2 Analyst — Incident Responder | Validated incident investigation, timeline construction, containment analysis |
| **T3** | Tier 3 Analyst — Advanced Threat | APT investigation, advanced TTP analysis, sophisticated attack chain reconstruction |

### 🔴 Incident Response (`03-incident-response/`)

| ID | Role | Capability |
|----|------|------------|
| **IR-L** | IR Lead / Incident Commander | Full incident command, stakeholder coordination, breach scope management |
| **IR-H** | IR Handler / Analyst | Containment execution, eradication steps, recovery actions |
| **DIR-IR** | Director of Incident Response | Program-level IR governance, major breach command authority |

### 🔬 Digital Forensics & IR (`04-dfir/`)

| ID | Role | Capability |
|----|------|------------|
| **DF** | DFIR Forensic Examiner | Disk and filesystem forensics, evidence preservation, chain of custody |
| **MF** | Memory Forensics Specialist | RAM analysis, process injection detection, in-memory artifact recovery |
| **NF** | Network Forensics Analyst | PCAP analysis, C2 identification, lateral movement path reconstruction |
| **MOB** | Mobile Forensics Specialist | iOS/Android acquisition, app data extraction, mobile artifact analysis |
| **ED** | eDiscovery Analyst | Legal hold coordination, data preservation, ESI collection |
| **DFIR-L** | DFIR Lead | Complex investigation command, team coordination, expert witness support |

### 🌐 Threat Intelligence & OSINT (`05-threat-intelligence/`)

| ID | Role | Capability |
|----|------|------------|
| **CTI** | Cyber Threat Intelligence Analyst | IOC enrichment, threat actor profiling, TTP mapping to MITRE ATT&CK |
| **OSI** | OSINT Analyst | External exposure discovery, leaked credential identification, infrastructure recon |
| **DW** | Dark Web Analyst | Darknet marketplace monitoring, threat actor forum tracking, credential leak detection |
| **DIR-TI** | Director of Threat Intelligence | Intelligence program strategy, fusion center coordination |

### ⚙️ Detection Engineering & SIEM (`06-siem-detection/`)

| ID | Role | Capability |
|----|------|------------|
| **DE** | Detection Engineer | Sigma, KQL, SPL, and YARA rule creation, detection gap analysis |
| **SE** | SIEM Engineer | Data source onboarding, parsing, normalization, SIEM health troubleshooting |
| **SO** | SOAR Engineer | Playbook design, automation logic, integration architecture |

### 🕵️ Proactive Security

