## About BluAgent

**BluAgent** is an AI governance and SOC automation platform built for mid-market cybersecurity teams. It combines real-time agentic runtime observability, immutable decision audit trails, and ISO 42001 / NIST AI RMF auditor-ready evidence packaging — purpose-built for organizations that need enterprise-grade AI security assurance without enterprise complexity.

- Website: [bluagent.io](https://bluagent.ai)
- Built by practitioners, for practitioners.

